last_posts_request.query:
query multiPostQuery($input: MultiPostInput) {
  posts(input: $input) {
    results {
      ...PostsListWithVotes
      __typename
    }
    totalCount
    __typename
  }
}

fragment PostsListWithVotes on Post {
  ...PostsList
  currentUserVote
  currentUserExtendedVote
  __typename
}

fragment PostsList on Post {
  ...PostsListBase
  deletedDraft
  contents {
    _id
    html
    plaintextDescription
    wordCount
    version
    __typename
  }
  fmCrosspost {
    isCrosspost
    hostedHere
    foreignPostId
    __typename
  }
  __typename
}
